Package de.bfs.radon.omsimulation.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OMBuilding
    Public class OMBuilding used for creating building meta-objects with custom name and all the rooms and cellars used in simulations later.
    OMCampaign
    Public class OMCampaign, defining the simulated campaigns and its attributes.
    OMHelper
    Public abstract class OMHelper providing helper methods for writing simulation logs and doing calculations.
    OMRoom
    Public class OMRoom, defining the important attributes for the room objects which are required for OMBuildings and OMCampaigns later.
    OMSimulation
    Public class OMSimulation used for creating simulation meta-objects with custom name and all the campaigns used for analysis later.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OMCampaignType
    Public enum OMCampaignType, identifying the total number of different rooms used in a campaign.
    OMRoomType
    Public enum OMRoomType, defining the required types of rooms: Cellar, Room, Misc.
